{"tid":1154812,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[堂堂正正] 無拘留必要性 勝利拘留令被駁回","createTime":"2019-05-14T13:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T14:27:33.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d26f28ba9aa6eaf1911690de0ae20308628b92eb","tid":1154812,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0067sxldly1g316ay6900j30so194wlm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F0067sxldly1g316ay6900j30so194wlm.jpg&h=f335c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14日,首爾中央地方法院負責簽發拘捕令的部長審判官申宗烈(音譯)說明了反駁拘捕令的理由:&quot;主要嫌疑人法人資金貪污部分與YuriHoldings控股公司及BurningSun法人的法律性質,股東構成,資金提取經過,資金使用原因等存在著爭議的餘地。&quot; 同時他還補充說&quot;剩下的嫌疑部分,根據嫌疑內容及說明程度,嫌疑人的參與範圍,包括嫌疑人審問等調查經過和期間收集的證據資料等,很難認定其為毀滅證據等拘留理由&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天佑OPPA"},{"pid":"61a10f6523c325a5704549eff66d0ae2aba58509","tid":1154812,"uid":20291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d26f28ba9aa6eaf1911690de0ae20308628b92eb","tid":1154812,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0067sxldly1g316ay6900j30so194wlm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F0067sxldly1g316ay6900j30so194wlm.jpg&h=f335c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14日,首爾中央地方法院負責簽發拘捕令的部長審判官申宗烈(音譯)說明了反駁拘捕令的理由:&quot;主要嫌疑人法人資金貪污部分與YuriHoldings控股公司及BurningSun法人的法律性質,股東構成,資金提取經過,資金使用原因等存在著爭議的餘地。&quot; 同時他還補充說&quot;剩下的嫌疑部分,根據嫌疑內容及說明程度,嫌疑人的參與範圍,包括嫌疑人審問等調查經過和期間收集的證據資料等,很難認定其為毀滅證據等拘留理由&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天佑OPPA"},"citedBy":0,"